<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4929162>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 5. Pararhinoleucophenga sylvatica sp. nov., male terminalia: A. Epandrium, surstylus, and cercus; B. surstyli, cerci and ventral processes of cercus (vp); C. hypandrium, vertical flaps of hypandrium, parameres, aedeagus and aedeagal apodeme. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4929162/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4929156>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 4. Pararhinoleucophenga amnicola sp. nov., male terminalia: A. Epandrium and cercus (lateral view); B. surstyli and cerci (posterior view); C. hypandrium (hypd), vertical flaps of hypandrium (fla), gonopods (gon), parameres (pm), aedeagus (aed), and aedeagal apodeme (aed a) (ventral view); D. ditto (lateral view). Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4929156/files/figure.png" .

